Privacy Policy — Meridian Tarot

Last updated: January 2026

Meridian Tarot is designed with sovereignty, simplicity, and user respect at its core. This app does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data—ever.

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information.We do not track you.We do not use analytics.We do not use cookies or identifiers.We do not request or store account information.

Device Permissions

Meridian Tarot does not request any device permissions beyond what is required for basic app functionality.The app works fully offline.

Third‑Party Services

The app uses no third‑party SDKs, analytics tools, ad networks, or cloud services.

Children’s Privacy

Because the app collects no data, it is safe for users of all ages.

Changes to This Policy

If the app ever changes to include optional features that require data, this policy will be updated. You will always be able to use the core app without sharing personal information.

Contact

If you have questions, you can reach the developer at:meridiangroupeapps@gmail.com

